text:
Checked out completely for a spell, apologies to all my mutuals for the autism. 
There's definitely a shut-in spiral. Gets awkward to break.
Return to the Internet after vast hiatus and the first thing I see is this. (Sorely tempted to just quit social reality terminally.) unz.com/article/curtis-yarvi…

... "... Now, two years after the fall of France to accelerationism, it appears that history approaches a turning point once more. ..." 
(Antonin Artaud is French President.)
Being in Seoul without the need for VPN hassle was enough of a jolt.
I can't possibly go that far.
